entries.s_10: We live in Coronet City. Ilyamo wanted to go hiking and the best hiking is around here. Their group disappeared 2 days ago.
entries.s_12: Do you have the route that he took?
entries.s_14: I don't, but he went with some group. I can give you the location of their base camp.
entries.s_16: Is there anything else you can tell me?
entries.s_18: Ilyamo is a tall human with dark hair and dark eyes. I'll show you a holo.
entries.s_20: Ok. I think I can recognize him. I'll go look for him now.
entries.s_25: Thank you so much! Ilyamo is safe and he will be back with me soon. I owe it all to you!
entries.s_6: I hope that Commander Talte sent you to me.
entries.s_8: He did. Please tell me what you can.
